WEBVTT 


1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.320
<div class="key" data-key="1">
<p><span class="cue" data-begin="00:00:00.010" data-end="00:00:03.390">Det kommer et romskip.</span></p>
</div>

2
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:14.520
<div class="key" data-key="2">
<p><span data-begin="00:00:03.390" data-end="00:00:06.520">Jenny er ei jente.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:06.520" data-end="00:00:09.630">Samir er en gutt.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:09.690" data-end="00:00:14.520">De er venner. De har en hage</span></p>
</div>

3
00:00:14.520 --> 00:00:37.200
<div class="key" data-key="3">
<p><span data-begin="00:00:14.520" data-end="00:00:17.860">- Sukkererter er godt, sa Jenny.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:17.860" data-end="00:00:22.400">- Vi kan så frø, så får vi mange.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:22.400" data-end="00:00:26.840">- Kræsj! Brak! Brekk! Knus!</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:26.840" data-end="00:00:30.180">Noe stort landet i treet.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:30.180" data-end="00:00:32.500">Det var ei kule.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:32.500" data-end="00:00:34.860">Var den av glass?</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:34.860" data-end="00:00:37.000">Var den farlig?</span></p>
</div>

4
00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:57.920
<div class="key" data-key="4">
<p><span data-begin="00:00:37.000" data-end="00:00:39.470">Noe falt ut.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:39.470" data-end="00:00:42.700">En person hang i ei grein.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:42.700" data-end="00:00:46.430">- En rar person, sa Jenny lavt.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:46.430" data-end="00:00:50.560">- Den har lange ører som en rev!</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:50.560" data-end="00:00:55.420">- En rar katt, sa Samir stille.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:00:55.420" data-end="00:00:57.900">- Den har sko!</span></p>
</div>

5
00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:13.020
<div class="key" data-key="5">
<p><span data-begin="00:00:57.900" data-end="00:01:00.900">Personen hoppet ned.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:00.900" data-end="00:01:03.520">Katta hoppet ned.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:03.520" data-end="00:01:06.840">Personen la handa over hjertet sitt</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:06.840" data-end="00:01:10.520">og sa: - Ikke vær redde.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:10.520" data-end="00:01:13.200">Vi kommer i fred.</span></p>
</div>

6
00:01:13.020 --> 00:01:28.960
<div class="key" data-key="6">
<p><span data-begin="00:01:13.200" data-end="00:01:15.680">- Jeg heter Hen.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:15.680" data-end="00:01:17.870">Dette er Katt.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:17.870" data-end="00:01:20.240">Vi har reist langt.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:20.240" data-end="00:01:22.300">Vi har reist forbi</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:22.300" data-end="00:01:26.170">Neptun, Uranus, Saturn,</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:26.170" data-end="00:01:28.980">Jupiter og Mars.</span></p>
</div>

7
00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:45.760
<div class="key" data-key="7">
<p><span data-begin="00:01:28.980" data-end="00:01:32.880">- Hvor kommer dere fra? spurte Samir.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:32.880" data-end="00:01:36.020">- Fra planeten Mo-lo.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:36.020" data-end="00:01:37.760">Vi har vann.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:37.760" data-end="00:01:41.310">Vi kan snakke og forstå alle språk.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:41.310" data-end="00:01:45.720">Sola vår heter Proxima Centauri.</span></p>
</div>

8
00:01:45.760 --> 00:02:04.600
<div class="key" data-key="8">
<p><span data-begin="00:01:45.720" data-end="00:01:50.110">- Den kula der er vel ikke sterk, sa Samir.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:50.110" data-end="00:01:52.040">- Jo, sa Hen.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:52.040" data-end="00:01:56.300">- Den er laget av gzi-gzy fra et fjell.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:01:56.300" data-end="00:02:01.260">Gzi-gzy betyr mu-lig på deres språk.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:01.260" data-end="00:02:04.600">Vi har reist med mu-lig.</span></p>
</div>

9
00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:16.100
<div class="key" data-key="9">
<p><span data-begin="00:02:04.600" data-end="00:02:07.320">- Ta på disse brillene, sa Hen.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:07.320" data-end="00:02:11.040">- De er laget av fjellet gzi-gzy.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:11.040" data-end="00:02:13.610">Jenny tok på seg brillene.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:13.610" data-end="00:02:16.200">Samir tok på seg brillene.</span></p>
</div>

10
00:02:16.100 --> 00:02:26.420
<div class="key" data-key="10">
<p><span data-begin="00:02:16.200" data-end="00:02:20.130">- Jeg ser et stort dyr! ropte Samir.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:20.130" data-end="00:02:23.660">Det er gult og brunt og har pels!</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:23.660" data-end="00:02:26.520">En bjørn som kan fly!</span></p>
</div>

11
00:02:26.420 --> 00:02:43.720
<div class="key" data-key="11">
<p><span data-begin="00:02:26.520" data-end="00:02:30.200">- Nå bader den i en stor blomst!</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:30.200" data-end="00:02:33.480">Blomsten drysser gult støv på den!</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:33.480" data-end="00:02:36.830">- Støvet er pollen, sa Hen.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:36.830" data-end="00:02:39.770">- Det kommer fra hannblomster.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:39.770" data-end="00:02:43.790">Eller gutter, hvis du skjønner det bedre.</span></p>
</div>

12
00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:58.280
<div class="key" data-key="12">
<p><span data-begin="00:02:43.790" data-end="00:02:46.820">- Nå sitter den på en gul blomst</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:46.820" data-end="00:02:49.720">på treet her! sa Jenny og pekte.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:49.720" data-end="00:02:54.690">Det er hundre gule stilker med kuler på.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:02:54.690" data-end="00:02:58.190">- Kulene har pollen, sa Hen.</span></p>
</div>

13
00:02:58.280 --> 00:03:13.900
<div class="key" data-key="13">
<p><span data-begin="00:02:58.190" data-end="00:03:02.020">- Mellom stilkene er det små grønne krukker,</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:02.020" data-end="00:03:04.960">sa Jenny. – Bjørnen har snabel.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:04.960" data-end="00:03:08.290">Nå suger den vann fra de grønne kulene.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:08.290" data-end="00:03:13.940">- Det er sukker-vann, sa Hen. – Nektar. Mat.</span></p>
</div>

14
00:03:13.900 --> 00:03:36.240
<div class="key" data-key="14">
<p><span data-begin="00:03:13.940" data-end="00:03:17.670">- Bjørn med snabel og vinger, lo Samir.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:17.670" data-end="00:03:20.050">- Er det en elefantbjørn?</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:20.050" data-end="00:03:24.060">- Blomsten rister gult støv på dyret, sa Jenny.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:24.060" data-end="00:03:28.730">- Dyret klør seg, så Samir. – Den børster seg!</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:28.730" data-end="00:03:32.440">- Hen sa: Dyret har kurver på beina.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:32.440" data-end="00:03:36.280">Det samler blomsterstøv. Mat.</span></p>
</div>

15
00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:43.500
<div class="key" data-key="15">
<p><span data-begin="00:03:36.280" data-end="00:03:38.480">Dyret fløy til treet</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:38.480" data-end="00:03:40.130">som sto ved stiden av.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:40.130" data-end="00:03:42.190">Der var det grønne blomster.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:42.190" data-end="00:03:43.520">Mange små.</span></p>
</div>

16
00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:58.220
<div class="key" data-key="16">
<p><span data-begin="00:03:43.520" data-end="00:03:45.660">Mellom blomstene var det</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:45.660" data-end="00:03:47.700">små grønne krukker med saft.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:47.700" data-end="00:03:51.090">Dyret sugde saft med snabelen sin.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:51.090" data-end="00:03:53.720">- Hunnblomster, sa Hen.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:53.720" data-end="00:03:56.500">- Eller jenter, om du skjønner det bedre.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:03:56.500" data-end="00:03:58.370">Mye saft.</span></p>
</div>

17
00:03:58.220 --> 00:04:16.880
<div class="key" data-key="17">
<p><span data-begin="00:03:58.370" data-end="00:04:02.330">Jenny så på dyret. Det gule støvet</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:02.330" data-end="00:04:07.520">på pelsen ble klint av på de grønne blomstene.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:07.520" data-end="00:04:11.810">Hen sa: -Blomsterstøv fra hannblomst</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:11.810" data-end="00:04:16.820">til hunn-blomst. Pollinering. Blir frø.</span></p>
</div>

18
00:04:16.880 --> 00:04:27.980
<div class="key" data-key="18">
<p><span data-begin="00:04:16.820" data-end="00:04:19.050">Dyret fløy vekk.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:19.050" data-end="00:04:22.340">- Nektar i magen og pollen i kurver,</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:22.340" data-end="00:04:24.600">sa Hen. - Mat for dyret.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:24.600" data-end="00:04:28.110">Mat for dem som skal bli nye dyr.</span></p>
</div>

19
00:04:27.980 --> 00:04:47.580
<div class="key" data-key="19">
<p><span data-begin="00:04:28.110" data-end="00:04:31.720">Jenny og Samir tok av seg brillene.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:31.720" data-end="00:04:35.160">- Hva var det vi så, sa Samir.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:35.160" data-end="00:04:39.200">- Der er det, smilte Hen og pekte.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:39.200" data-end="00:04:42.130">De så bare ei humle.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:42.130" data-end="00:04:47.500">- He? Vanlig humle og vanlig seljeblomst?</span></p>
</div>

20
00:04:47.580 --> 00:05:07.860
<div class="key" data-key="20">
<p><span data-begin="00:04:47.500" data-end="00:04:52.480">- Vanlig? sa Hen. - Hva er vanlig?</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:52.480" data-end="00:04:55.930">Ikke noe å bry seg om, tenker du?</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:04:55.930" data-end="00:05:00.210">Men hvis du ser, virkelig ser,</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:00.210" data-end="00:05:02.970">da skjer det merkelige ting.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:02.970" data-end="00:05:05.500">Kanskje du kan se det,</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:05.500" data-end="00:05:07.940">uten disse brillene?</span></p>
</div>

21
00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:33.380
<div class="key" data-key="21">
<p><span data-begin="00:05:07.940" data-end="00:05:10.850">Katt sa ingenting.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:10.850" data-end="00:05:13.400">Katt skrudde på skruer og hjul</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:13.400" data-end="00:05:15.160">i beltet sitt.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:15.160" data-end="00:05:21.120">Jenny spurte: Men hvorfor kom dere hit?</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:21.120" data-end="00:05:25.960">Hen smilte og sa: - Dere får vite det.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:25.960" data-end="00:05:29.600">Siden. Vær tålmodig.</span></p>
<p><span data-begin="00:05:29.600" data-end="00:05:31.970">Tiden er din venn.</span></p>
</div>
